long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: VelocityInsight brings the power of Velocity Automotive to your store’s CRM or IMS. With a simple click you power on the VelocityInsight tool inside your inventory management system to highlight and then select VIN numbers to view their status and key stats in Velocity Automotive.
